data.description: If you have always dreamed of Home Steading, this place is for you. A peaceful feeling comes over you as you drive the long driveway home. With 26+acres, you can have a milk cow, some chickens, a garden, all you need for home steading. Or have someone else make the hay and just enjoy the views. 1865 home built to last, has the features that take you back to another time, with modern conveniences. New Ac. New Septic.
